    public class MaterialDatePicker
extends MaterialWidget
implements HasGrid, HasError, HasOrientation, HasPlaceholder, com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasValue<Date>, com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.HasOpenHandlers<MaterialDatePicker>, com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.HasCloseHandlers<MaterialDatePicker>
    Material Date Picker will provide a visual calendar to your apps.

    UiBinder Usage:

    <m:MaterialDatePicker ui:field="datePicker">

    Java Usage:

    datePicker.setDate(new Date());
    Author:
    kevzlou7979, Ben Dol
    See Also:
    Material Date Picker
